<!--
  OpenEmuARM64 core list
  ======================
  Points to the original OpenEmu-Update appcast URLs for cores that are
  confirmed universal binaries (x86_64 + arm64).

  Cores marked [x86 only] are excluded until ARM64 builds are available.
  See: https://github.com/bazley82/OpenEmuARM64/issues (medium-term tracking issue)

  ARM64 status verified: 2026-03-20
    universal (arm64 + x86_64): Nestopia, mGBA, Gambatte, Genesis Plus, Snes9x, FCEU, ProSystem
    x86 only — excluded:        BSNES, DeSmuME, Mednafen, Stella, Atari800, O2EM,
                                 Picodrive, Mupen64Plus, Bliss, VecXGL, CrabEmu
-->
<cores>

